# Key Design Principles

The repository is built around several core design principles.

### Deterministic kernels

GPU kernels are designed to produce reproducible financial results.

### Blittable GPU models

All GPU data structures use layouts compatible with direct memory transfer.

### Portfolio-level parallelism

Each contract is evaluated independently on separate GPU threads.

### Separation of concerns

* Domain models remain CPU-side.
* GPU models are specialized for parallel execution.

